    de.dfki.omm.events
    Classes employed with events and event handling on the OMS.
    de.dfki.omm.impl
    Concrete implementations of OMMs, different block types, and their handling.
    de.dfki.omm.impl.rest
    Concrete implementations of OMMs, different block types, and their handling for the REST interface.
    de.dfki.omm.interfaces
    Interfaces describing structure and functionality of various implementing classes.
    de.dfki.omm.tools
    Tools and helpers for OMS functionality, such as XML handling or codec definition.
    de.dfki.omm.types
    Various special data types used throughout the OMS.
